query:
INSERT INTO products (name, slug, description, story, categoryId, `condition`, suggestedPrice, minimumPrice, maximumPrice, sevaTokenPrice, brand, size, color, material, sku, quantity, status, source, donorName, isFeatured, isChildrenFree, createdAt, updatedAt) VALUES
('Vintage Denim Jacket', 'vintage-denim-jacket-001', 'Classic denim jacket with beautiful patina. Perfect for layering.', 'Donated by a fashion designer who wore this jacket during her college years in the 90s.', 1, 'good', 15000, 8000, 25000, 3, 'Levis', 'M', 'Blue', '100% Cotton Denim', 'CLO-001-VDJ', 1, 'available', 'donation', 'Priya M.', true, false, NOW(), NOW()),
('Childrens Picture Book Set', 'childrens-picture-books-002', 'Set of 5 colorful picture books perfect for ages 3-7.', 'These books were read every night to two siblings who have now grown up.', 2, 'excellent', 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BOOK-002-CPB', 1, 'available', 'donation', 'Sharma Family', true, true, NOW(), NOW()),
('Handwoven Cotton Rug', 'handwoven-cotton-rug-003', 'Beautiful handwoven rug in earth tones. 4x6 feet.', 'Crafted by artisans in Rajasthan, this rug was part of a home for 10 years.', 3, 'good', 20000, 12000, 35000, 4, NULL, NULL, 'Multi-color', '100% Cotton', 'HOME-003-HCR', 1, 'available', 'donation', 'Mehta Residence', true, false, NOW(), NOW()),
('Wooden Building Blocks', 'wooden-building-blocks-004', 'Set of 50 natural wooden blocks in various shapes.', 'These blocks helped three children learn shapes, colors, and creativity.', 4, 'excellent', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Handmade', NULL, NULL, 'Natural Wood', 'TOY-004-WBB', 1, 'available', 'donation', 'Anonymous', true, true, NOW(), NOW()),
('Ceramic Tea Set', 'ceramic-tea-set-005', 'Elegant ceramic tea set with teapot and 4 cups.', 'This tea set was a wedding gift that has hosted countless conversations.', 3, 'excellent', 12000, 7000, 20000, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ceramic', 'HOME-005-CTS', 1, 'available', 'donation', 'Kumar Family', true, false, NOW(), NOW()),
('Yoga Mat & Block Set', 'yoga-mat-block-set-006', 'Barely used yoga mat with matching block.', 'Purchased with the best intentions during New Years resolutions.', 3, 'excellent', 8000, 5000, 15000, 2, 'Decathlon', NULL, 'Purple', 'TPE', 'HOME-006-YMB', 1, 'available', 'donation', 'Anjali R.', true, false, NOW(), NOW()),
('Classic Literature Collection', 'classic-literature-collection-007', 'Set of 10 classic novels including Jane Austen, Dickens, and Tolstoy.', 'A literature professors personal collection, carefully curated over decades.', 2, 'good', 18000, 10000, 30000, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BOOK-007-CLC', 1, 'available', 'donation', 'Dr. Patel', true, false, NOW(), NOW()),
('Kids Bicycle', 'kids-bicycle-008', 'Sturdy bicycle with training wheels. Red and white color.', 'This bicycle taught a child to ride, fall, get up, and try again.', 4, 'good', 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hero', '16 inch', 'Red & White', NULL, 'TOY-008-KBC', 1, 'available', 'donation', 'Desai Family', true, true, NOW(), NOW())
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE name=name
